POST /support → ticket created with auto-assigned agent & priority by category
Ticket saved with TKT-XXXXXXXX reference
Agent notified (mock log) → status IN_PROGRESS
User acknowledgement sent (mock log) with ticket reference
Admin manages via /support/admin/** endpoints
🌐 API Gateway
Route: Path=/support/** → lb://SUPPORT-SERVICE
Circuit breaker: supportCircuitBreaker
Swagger: http://localhost:8087/swagger-ui.html or via gateway at http://localhost:8080/support/swagger-ui.html